com.simbachain.simba

Class CallReturn<R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simbachain.simba.CallResponse
      • com.simbachain.simba.CallReturn<R>

  • public class CallReturn<R>
extends CallResponse
    The return value of a call to a method using POST that contains return data. The response contains a unique request identifier. This can either be an ID generated for the request, or a transaction hash associated with the request if the request is creating a trasnaction.

    Additionally the response may contain a state attribute and an error string.
